reviewText:
I cant rate it because disc 3 is missing... what the hell i really go crazy. All i watned to do is watch the Telenovela again and now there are disc missing.

...

Great, great soap! one of the best ever made in Colombia, very realistic!
All thou the DVD i got said it was in "very good" conditions which was not true, DVD # 5 didn't even play and the rest of the DVD's were all scratch!! It took me longer to try to make the DVD's work than to watch the series. Thanks
